NAME
    Log::ger::Level::Like::PythonLogging - Define logging levels like
    Python's logging facility

VERSION
    version 0.001

SYNOPSIS
     # load before 'use Log::ger' in any package/target
     use Log::ger::Level::Like::PythonLogging;

DESCRIPTION
    This module changes the Log::ger levels to:

        notset => 0,
        critical => 10,
        error => 20,
        warning => 30,
        info => 40,
        debug => 50,

SEE ALSO
    [1] https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.html

